From 91a8a673ec7f2034391c476e51b82a81501a39db Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alexander Hoffman <alxhoff@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 23 Mar 2026 09:44:59 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 27/32] Device tree: Fix D457 line_length and improve camera
 port documentation

- Fix D457 line_length from "1280" to "2200" for all 8 camera modes
  to match the actual sensor timing and prevent CSI CRC errors
- Replace legacy comments with clear documentation mapping each
  camera group to its CSI port and deserializer
- Add section headers for D457 and ISX031 camera groups
---
 ...4-p3737-0000-camera-d4xx-quad-sw-v1_1.dtsi | 36 +++++++++++++------
 1 file changed, 25 insertions(+), 11 deletions(-)

diff --git a/hardware/nvidia/platform/t23x/concord/kernel-dts/cvb/tegra234-p3737-0000-camera-d4xx-quad-sw-v1_1.dtsi b/hardware/nvidia/platform/t23x/concord/kernel-dts/cvb/tegra234-p3737-0000-camera-d4xx-quad-sw-v1_1.dtsi
